<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb</title>
<lyrics>[C1]
   ạlqrạr
   qṣẗ ạlḥb ạlʿjyb
   qd tjlt fy ạlṣlyb
   qd rwạhạ fy ḥbyby
   sạʿẗ ạlṣmt ạlrhyb
   whw msḥwq ạlfw̉ạd
   whw mjrwḥ ạljbyn
   qd rwạhạ fy ḥbyby
   bạldm ạlgẖạly ạltẖmyn

[V1]
 1 - kạn bạlạ̉ms yjwl
 yṣnʿ ạlkẖyr ạlʿẓym
 wynạdy bạlḥyạẗi
 ysẖfy jrḥ ạlmtʿbyn
 (kạn ḥbh ʿjybạ
 ạ̹dẖ ạ̉ḥb ạlậtẖmyn
 dẖạ lạ̉nh yswʿu
 qd ạ̉ḥb kl ḥyn)2

[V2]
 2 - bynmạ ạlḥb yjwl
 kạn fkr ạlḥạqdyn
 kyf yqtlwạ yswʿa
 ạ̹dẖ ạ̉ḥb ạlmdẖnbyn
 (ḥty̱ tnthy ạlrwạyh
 qṣẗ ạlḥb ạltẖmyn
 ḥty̱ tuktba ạlnhạyh
 mạt byn ạlmjrmyn)2

[V3]
 3 - qd ạủhyn ạlḥbũ ẓlmạ
 qd ạủhyn bạlṣlyb
 mnṭqu ạlnạs tlạsẖy̱
 ạ̹dẖ bdạ ạlḥb ạlskyb
 (ạ̹nh ḥb sybqy̱
 ạ̉bd ạldhr ykwn
 lys ḥb mtẖlu hdẖạ
 ṣạdquⁿ dwmạ ḥnwn)2

[V4]
 4 - ạ̉yũ ḥbiⁿ̃ qd tnạhy̱
 mtẖlu ḥbh ạlʿjyb
 ạ̉y ḥb mtẖl hdẖạ
 qd bdạ bʿd ạlṣlyb
 (kl ḥb fy ạlwjwd
 nbʿh ḥb yswʿ
 ạ̉y ḥb fy kyạny
 rdũh ḥb yswʿ)2</lyrics>
